      "home.about.longTitle": "The Ultimate Collection of Developer Tools",
      "home.about.longDesc": "DevToolz is a comprehensive, privacy-first platform designed to simplify the daily tasks of developers, designers, and IT professionals. Leveraging advanced Client-Side Processing architecture, including WebAssembly (Wasm) and the standard Web Crypto API (window.crypto), we ensure that resource-intensive operations—from parsing complex large JSON payloads to applying high-efficiency lossless image compression—are executed securely within your local environment.\n\nBy decentralizing computation to your local machine via Pure JS local computation, we eliminate network transmission latency and guarantee cryptographic security for your sensitive API tokens, source code, and configurations. Experience fast algorithmic processing and robust statistical text analysis without ever transmitting a single byte to remote servers. Modern engineering workflows demand uncompromised performance and verifiable zero-knowledge privacy—DevToolz delivers both by utilizing strict client-side DOM processing.",

      "json.title": "JSON Formatter",
      "json.seoTitle": "JSON Formatter | Free Online Formatting Tool",
      "json.desc": "Format and validate JSON data easily.",
      "json.longDesc.title": "About JSON Formatter",
      "json.longDesc.p1": "This tool is a free online **JSON Formatter** that helps you organize, beautify, and validate complex JSON data instantly. It is widely used by developers when working with APIs or configuration files.",
      "json.longDesc.p2": "Simply paste your raw text, and it will automatically indent and structure the data, making it highly readable. If there are syntax errors, it highlights the exact location, saving you valuable debugging time.",
      "json.longDesc.p3": "By using this fast and secure **JSON Formatter**, you can quickly understand your data structure and significantly boost your development productivity.",
      "json.longDesc.p4": "Technical Specifications & Client-Side Execution (Performance Metrics): This tool operates exclusively within your local browser environment. By utilizing advanced Pure JS local computation and standard Web APIs, all algorithmic operations—including parsing, formatting, and mathematical evaluations—are executed locally at the node level. This ensures that no sensitive data is ever transmitted across the network, completely avoiding the overhead of external HTTP requests. By strictly adhering to these client-side principles, we provide a zero-latency, cryptographically secure environment for developers handling confidential payloads. The robust technical architecture guarantees 100% data sovereignty and prevents potential interception vectors such as MITM attacks.",
      "json.longDesc.p5": "Optimization & Industry Standards (Web Crypto API & Wasm Ready): Engineered for high performance, this utility leverages highly optimized DOM rendering and modern algorithmic structures (such as window.crypto for secure entropy and WebAssembly structural methodologies where applicable). It handles extensive input vectors scaling up to large sizes with high efficiency. The integrated backend logic relies on precise mathematical compliance and industry-standard protocols, guaranteeing high-fidelity outputs for enterprise environments. This professional-grade tooling enables IT professionals to implement strict data validation, seamless transformations, and rigorous network-free security.",
