      "pass.desc": "Generate strong, secure passwords instantly.",
      "pass.longDesc.title": "About Password Generator",
      "pass.longDesc.p1": "This tool is a free online **Password Generator** that creates highly secure and random passwords based on your specific requirements. It is essential when signing up for new websites or updating existing passwords to enhance security.",
