      "text.title": "Text Counter",
      "text.seoTitle": "Text Counter | Free Online Word & Character Counter",
      "text.desc": "Count characters, words, and lines in real-time.",
      "text.longDesc.title": "About Text Counter",
      "text.longDesc.p1": "This tool is a free online **Text Counter** that accurately calculates the total length, word count, and character count (with or without spaces) of your text in real-time.",
