      "markdown.title": "Markdown Editor",
      "markdown.seoTitle": "Markdown Editor | Live Preview, GFM Support",
      "markdown.desc": "A powerful Markdown Editor with live preview and GitHub Flavored Markdown (GFM) support. See your rendered output instantly as you type.",
