      "hash.title": "Hash Generator",
      "hash.seoTitle": "Hash Generator | Free Online Tool",
      "hash.desc": "A free online tool to encrypt text or files using various hash algorithms like MD5 and SHA-256.",
      "hash.longDesc.title": "About Hash Generator",
      "hash.longDesc.p1": "This tool is a free online **Hash Generator** that securely encrypts and verifies the integrity of text strings or files. It perfectly supports various hash algorithms widely used in development and security fields, including MD5, SHA-1, SHA-256, SHA-512, SHA-3, and RIPEMD-160.",
      "hash.longDesc.p2": "Beyond simple text hashing, it offers HMAC (Hash-based Message Authentication Code) generation using a secret key to meet stronger security requirements. You can also calculate hashes for large files directly in your browser and choose to output the results in Hex or Base64 format, making it highly versatile.",
      "hash.longDesc.p3": "All hash calculations are performed locally in your browser, meaning your input text or file data is never transmitted to external servers, allowing you to handle sensitive information with peace of mind. Perform data security and integrity verification tasks quickly and safely with this expert-level Hash Generator.",
